01:16.442 --> 01:20.777
Fifi and Fin live with their
parents, Mama and Papa Fish,

01:20.779 --> 01:22.946
in a colorful coral house

01:22.948 --> 01:25.907
surrounded by green,
squishy seaweed

01:25.909 --> 01:29.413
in the fabulous, fun-filled
Fishtale Reef.

01:30.999 --> 01:33.124
It's the first day of school

01:33.126 --> 01:36.044
and Fifi and Finn
are very excited.

01:37.296 --> 01:42.383
Fifi, an adorable pink-colored
fish with long eyelashes,

01:42.385 --> 01:45.970
wears a shiny pink bow
on her head.

01:45.972 --> 01:48.431
How do I look, Fin?

01:48.433 --> 01:52.309
Her brother Fin,
a handsome blue-colored fish,

01:52.311 --> 01:56.187
wears oversized eyeglasses
and a baseball hat

01:56.189 --> 01:59.149
he found lying on
the ocean floor.

01:59.151 --> 02:01.068
Swishy, cute, and big.

02:01.070 --> 02:02.485
How about me?

02:02.487 --> 02:04.990
Ooh, fish-boppin' fantastic!

02:06.826 --> 02:08.324
I like your hat.

02:08.327 --> 02:09.533
Thanks, sis.

02:09.536 --> 02:11.871
Gotta look cool on the
first day of school.

02:11.873 --> 02:14.540
I'm a little nervous.

02:14.542 --> 02:15.665
About what?

02:15.667 --> 02:18.753
Well, about seeing
all my friends,

02:18.755 --> 02:21.757
about who my teacher
is going to be.

02:24.928 --> 02:27.510
Happy day, my little fishies,

02:27.512 --> 02:29.014
Happy day, Mama.

02:33.852 --> 02:35.685
Ready for the
first day of school?

02:35.687 --> 02:38.855
I'm ready,
but Fifi is nervous.

02:38.857 --> 02:41.399
Why are you nervous, Fifi?

02:41.401 --> 02:43.694
I haven't seen my
friends all summer.

02:43.696 --> 02:45.195
Will they remember me?

02:45.197 --> 02:47.323
Who will my teacher be?

02:47.325 --> 02:48.950
It's okay to feel nervous

02:48.952 --> 02:51.535
on your first day of school,
Fifi.

02:51.537 --> 02:53.371
Everyone does.

02:53.373 --> 02:55.873
Soon you'll be
having so much fun,

02:55.875 --> 02:58.542
all those nervous
feelings will wash away.

02:58.544 --> 02:59.919
How are you feeling, Fin?

02:59.921 --> 03:01.212
I'm excited.

03:01.214 --> 03:04.339
I'm gonna see my best
friend Sammie Swordfish,

03:04.341 --> 03:06.926
the coolest fish in the sea.

03:08.054 --> 03:10.887
I thought I was the
coolest fish in the sea.

03:10.889 --> 03:13.724
I'm so proud of you two.

03:13.726 --> 03:15.100
Ready to go?

03:15.102 --> 03:16.226
Yes!

03:18.356 --> 03:21.064
Every year on
the first day of school,

03:21.066 --> 03:25.820
Mama and Papa Fish swim Fifi
and Fin to the edge of the reef

03:25.822 --> 03:30.741
where ocean rock coves become
fish-filled classrooms.

03:30.743 --> 03:32.242
Lily!

03:32.244 --> 03:34.579
Look, it's my best friend Lily.

03:34.581 --> 03:37.333
Thanks for swimming
me to school.

03:38.917 --> 03:40.542
Sammie!

03:40.544 --> 03:42.587
See you later, alligators.

03:42.589 --> 03:44.921
Have a fun morning at school.

03:44.923 --> 03:48.510
We'll be here to swim
you home for lunch.

03:49.345 --> 03:52.597
Lily, it's so good to see you.

03:52.599 --> 03:54.265
How was your summer?

03:54.267 --> 03:56.850
My grandparents were awesome.

03:56.852 --> 04:00.313
We ate delicious
food all the time.

04:00.315 --> 04:01.772
How was your summer?

04:02.733 --> 04:03.734
Super fun.

04:04.776 --> 04:07.738
We played lots of
games in the reef.

04:08.739 --> 04:10.657
Oh look, there's Pedal!

04:11.784 --> 04:13.870
Pedal, how was your trip?

04:14.828 --> 04:16.245
It was amazing.

04:17.789 --> 04:20.123
Did you get to walk on land?

04:20.125 --> 04:22.000
What was it like?

04:22.002 --> 04:24.462
I did walk on land.

04:24.464 --> 04:26.507
It was a very sandy beach

04:27.425 --> 04:30.178
and the sand
tickled my flippers.

04:32.262 --> 04:34.638
This is so much fun.

04:34.640 --> 04:36.391
I love being friends.

04:37.560 --> 04:40.977
Fifi has forgotten
all about being nervous.

04:40.979 --> 04:43.940
She is too busy having fun.

04:48.488 --> 04:50.820
It's Principal
Bellowing Whale.

04:50.822 --> 04:53.073
School's about to begin.

04:53.075 --> 04:55.618
Who do you think we'll
get for our teacher?

04:55.620 --> 04:57.953
I hope it's Professor Shark.

04:57.955 --> 04:59.330
Me too!

04:59.332 --> 05:03.875
My dad says he's the
smartest shark in the sea.

05:03.877 --> 05:05.335
As little
fish laugh

05:05.337 --> 05:07.046
and play in the school park,

05:07.048 --> 05:11.302
they all hope their new
teacher is Professor Shark.

05:12.844 --> 05:16.681
As the early morning sunshine
beats down in the sea,

05:16.683 --> 05:21.644
the young fish wait to hear
who their teacher will be.

