05:39.497 --> 05:40.331
Lily.

05:41.248 --> 05:42.748
That's me!

05:42.750 --> 05:44.207
Fifi.

05:44.209 --> 05:46.460
We're together!

05:46.462 --> 05:48.044
Pedal.

05:48.046 --> 05:48.839
Trigger.

05:49.841 --> 05:51.423
Kiki.

