Sammie.

05:52.801 --> 05:53.635
Tang.

05:54.553 --> 05:59.517
And lastly, Diesel, Chopper,
and Fin.

06:00.142 --> 06:00.976
Oh no.

06:02.019 --> 06:04.187
My brother is in my class.

06:05.397 --> 06:10.109
All 10 of you
report to the classroom.

06:10.111 --> 06:12.277
Your teacher will be...

06:17.452 --> 06:19.120
Oh, Professor Shark.

06:23.332 --> 06:25.582
The 10
classmates gather around

06:25.584 --> 06:29.378
Professor Shark, a kind
and thoughtful teacher

06:29.380 --> 06:32.380
and the smartest
shark in the sea.

06:32.382 --> 06:35.967
Five fish bob on one
side of Professor Shark,

06:35.969 --> 06:38.346
five fish on the other,

06:38.348 --> 06:41.765
all of them thrilled
to be in his class.

06:41.767 --> 06:42.601
Welcome!

06:43.894 --> 06:47.979
I'm so happy to have
all of you in my class.

06:47.981 --> 06:49.899
Since it's the first
day of school,

06:49.901 --> 06:52.400
I'd like each of you to
tell us your name

06:52.402 --> 06:55.613
and something
special about yourself.

06:55.615 --> 06:56.950
I will go first.

06:58.116 --> 07:00.116
I am Professor Shark.

07:00.118 --> 07:03.537
I have thousands of
sharp teeth in my mouth,

07:03.539 --> 07:05.415
but I am very friendly.

07:06.793 --> 07:11.753
I have been teaching for many
years and I love what I do.

07:11.755 --> 07:14.800
I am very excited to
meet all of you.

07:15.885 --> 07:18.426
My name if Fifi.

07:18.428 --> 07:21.933
I am a pastel fish with big
goldfish eyes.

07:23.017 --> 07:24.808
Is that special?

07:24.810 --> 07:26.726
Yes, it is.

07:26.728 --> 07:28.604
What is your favorite color?

07:28.606 --> 07:30.106
Pink.

07:30.108 --> 07:32.442
As you can see, I love pink.

07:36.363 --> 07:39.698
I'm Fifi's brother and
I'm a blue pastel fish

07:39.700 --> 07:41.618
with big goldfish eyes.

07:42.495 --> 07:43.995
Yes, you are.

07:43.997 --> 07:46.621
What do you want to be
when you grow up, Fin?

07:46.623 --> 07:48.082
A scientist.

07:48.084 --> 07:50.209
I like learning about the sea.

07:50.211 --> 07:51.835
That's wonderful.

07:51.837 --> 07:56.173
The ocean is filled with so
many amazing things to discover.

07:56.175 --> 07:58.551
That makes you very special,
Fin.

07:58.553 --> 07:59.510
I'm Lily.

07:59.512 --> 08:00.971
I am a blue whale.

08:01.889 --> 08:03.638
Whales are not fish.

08:03.640 --> 08:04.890
We are mammals.

08:04.892 --> 08:06.393
I can breathe air.

08:07.896 --> 08:12.731
I love to eat and I'm going
to be very big when I grow up.

08:12.733 --> 08:15.234
And Lily is my best friend.

08:15.236 --> 08:17.861
Oh and Fifi's my best friend.

08:17.863 --> 08:19.697
Nice to meet you, Lily.

08:19.699 --> 08:22.952
Whales are very
special marine mammals.

08:23.911 --> 08:26.203
My name is Pedal.

08:26.205 --> 08:27.581
I'm a sea turtle.

08:28.541 --> 08:30.668
Sea turtles are reptiles.

08:32.044 --> 08:34.587
I can breathe underwater.

08:34.589 --> 08:37.380
I can also crawl onto land

08:37.381 --> 08:41.885
and let my hard turtle
shell soak up some sun.

08:41.886 --> 08:45.224
I want to be a detective when I
grow up.

08:46.059 --> 08:49.769
Being a detective is a very
special job.

08:49.771 --> 08:52.938
I bet you are one smart turtle.

08:52.940 --> 08:57.235
I'm Sammie Swordfish, the
coolest fish in the sea.

08:57.237 --> 09:01.572
Chop, chop, I have a really
cool sword as a nose.

09:01.574 --> 09:05.492
I can swim really fast
and I like to tell jokes.

09:08.790 --> 09:11.874
Telling jokes is a very
special talent.

09:11.876 --> 09:15.377
I look forward to hearing
some of your jokes, Sammie.

09:15.379 --> 09:18.255
I'm Kiki, a pufferfish.

09:18.257 --> 09:21.886
I can blow my body up
into a big round ball.

09:22.804 --> 09:26.429
I have a lot of sharp spikes on
my body.

09:26.431 --> 09:29.433
I love to play ocean soccer.

09:29.435 --> 09:31.851
I like to play soccer too.

09:31.853 --> 09:35.356
Playing sports is a
very special skill.

09:35.358 --> 09:36.399
I'm Diesel.

09:36.401 --> 09:37.732
I'm a Manta ray.

09:37.734 --> 09:42.779
I have a really flat body,
so I can swim super fast.

09:42.781 --> 09:45.283
I want to be a singer.

09:48.246 --> 09:50.037
♪ Yeah ♪

09:50.039 --> 09:52.125
What a beautiful voice.

09:53.459 --> 09:56.751
Singing is a very
special talent.

09:56.753 --> 09:58.169
I'm Chopper.

09:58.171 --> 10:00.757
I have really big, sharp teeth.

10:01.593 --> 10:05.760
But like Professor
Shark, I'm friendly too.

10:05.762 --> 10:10.435
I want to be a deep sea diver
and find buried treasures.

10:13.438 --> 10:15.103
Wow!

10:15.105 --> 10:16.731
Buried treasure?

10:16.733 --> 10:18.151
That sounds cool.

10:19.735 --> 10:21.069
Hi, I'm Trigger.

10:21.988 --> 10:24.322
I'm a very special fish.

10:24.324 --> 10:26.741
I have a head
shaped like a horse

10:26.743 --> 10:31.662
and a really cool tail that
I can wrap around seaweed.

10:31.664 --> 10:33.872
I want to be a teacher when I
grow up.

10:34.709 --> 10:37.250
An adventurer and a teacher!

10:37.252 --> 10:39.544
Very special careers.

10:39.546 --> 10:40.795
I'm Tang.

10:40.797 --> 10:42.716
I'm a yellow tang fish.

10:44.009 --> 10:48.596
I have a really cool
head-fin feathery crest.

10:48.598 --> 10:51.348
I want to be a fish groomer.

10:51.350 --> 10:52.515
Thank you, Tang.

10:52.517 --> 10:55.561
Grooming other fish is
a special talent too.

10:55.563 --> 10:58.396
What an interesting
group of fish.

11:00.526 --> 11:02.901
Ah, that's the lunch bell, kids.

11:02.903 --> 11:04.861
Well, I'm really looking forward

11:04.863 --> 11:06.905
to teaching you all this year.

11:09.160 --> 11:13.246
As the new sun
casts shadows on Fishtale Reef,

11:13.248 --> 11:16.166
the fish swim home
to talk and eat.

11:22.674 --> 11:25.216
As Principal Whale's
voice bellow

11:25.218 --> 11:27.175
an underwater punch,

11:27.177 --> 11:31.056
everyone in Fishtale Reef
swims home for lunch.

11:35.936 --> 11:37.812
You must be hungry.

11:37.814 --> 11:39.396
Let's have some lunch.

11:39.398 --> 11:42.732
Then I want to hear
all about school.

11:42.734 --> 11:44.360
Yes, let's hurry home.

11:44.362 --> 11:46.361
There's a fish football
match on TV.

11:46.363 --> 11:48.365
I don't want to miss it.

11:54.247 --> 11:58.415
Now that we've all eaten,
tell us all about your morning.

11:59.252 --> 12:02.252
Fin and I are
in the same class.

12:02.254 --> 12:04.212
Did you hear that, Papa?

12:04.214 --> 12:07.592
Fin and Fifi are
in the same class.

12:07.594 --> 12:09.427
Papa is
so busy watching

12:09.429 --> 12:11.261
the fish football match,

12:11.263 --> 12:14.807
